videos.headline: Rutgers spikes ball, loses game
videos.description: Rutgers QB Chris Laviano loses track of downs and intentionally spikes the ball on the fourth down with three seconds remaining, giving Michigan State the win.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rutgers spikes ball, loses game) 2015/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers' blunder seals the win for Michigan State
videos.description: Down 31-24 in the final seconds of the fourth quarter, Rutgers QB Chris Laviano spikes the ball on fourth down, giving Michigan State a 6-0 start to the season.
